name: Humankind : Forked
description:
This work represents whitelist to an upcoming heafnoire 1024 mint project on Ethereum; 'Humankind : Forked'

The series will explore pivotal moments in Humankind's history that forked our existence, for better or worse.

Supporters of any of my previous works are whitelisted (for free mint[+gas]) will also be aid-dropped this NFT (up to 100 collectors total) up until the end of October 2021, 

My hope is that airdropped/whitelisted addressees sell on secondary for 'peanuts' to help proliferate the project.

Wallets holding the NFT at time of 'Humankind : Forked.' launch will be awarded white listing for free mint [+gas].

NB: If you were airdropped this, you can sell freely; you're already whitelisted. Thanks for you support!
